# Front-end conventions

## Stack

Nuxt 3 (`ssr: false`), Vue 3, Pinia, `@nuxt/ui`, Tailwind (via Nuxt UI). Source root: `src/app/`.

## API access

Use `repository/modules/*.ts` via the repository factory — do not add ad-hoc `fetch` in components.

| Module | Domain |
| ------ | ------ |
| `labs.ts` | Laboratories |
| `omics-runs.ts`, `omics-workflows.ts` | HealthOmics |
| `seqera-runs.ts`, `seqera-pipelines.ts` | Seqera / Tower |
| `data-collections.ts` | Data collections & sequence sets |
| `file.ts`, `uploads.ts` | S3 file operations |

## Components

Shared UI uses `EG` prefix (`EGTable.vue`, `EGDashboard.vue`, …). Match existing composition API + `<script setup>` style.

## Styling

Global SCSS in `src/app/styles/`. Use `@nuxt/ui` components where siblings do.

## Config

Runtime settings from `config/easy-genomics.yaml` (deploy) / `env.nuxt.config` (local). Do not hardcode API base URLs.
